(88, 4, '2013-05-27 15:56:02', '2013-05-27 07:56:02', '<a href="http://thweb.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/productfinal.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-209" alt="productfinal" src="http://thweb.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/productfinal.png" width="750" height="250" /></a>\n\nWe’ve released our newest update on the Apple App Store! View it here: <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/sg/app/tradehero-mobile/id572226383?mt=8">https://itunes.apple.com/sg/app/tradehero-mobile/id572226383?mt=8</a>.\n\nNew features include:\n\n<strong>Most Skilled Leaderboard</strong>: Our new custom algorithm selects only the best and most skilled traders,making it easier for you to find and follow top Quality heroes.\n\n<strong>Stock Alerts</strong>: Get instant notifications when a stock hits your target price or moves by a desired percentage. Tap the Add Alert button on the stock screen.\n\n<strong>People search</strong>: The updated search bar now allows you to look up users by name\n\n<!--more-->\n\nTell us what you think about our update by commenting here, tweeting @TradeHeroMobile, posting on Facebook (<a href="http://www.facebook.com/TradeHero">www.facebook.com/TradeHero</a>) or writing to us (<a href="mailto:support@tradehero.mobi">support@tradehero.mobi</a>).\n\nAs the American economist Larry Summers once said, “<em>Most investors want to do today what they should have done yesterday.”</em>\n\nIt’s time to start trading and practising! Download TradeHero version 1.4 today.', 'Updates in Version 1.4', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'updates-in-version-1-4', '', '', '2013-05-27 15:56:02', '2013-05-27 07:56:02', '', 0, 'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=88', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(130, 4, '2013-06-13 18:34:46', '2013-06-13 10:34:46', '<a href="http://thweb.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/blog3.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-178" alt="blog3" src="http://thweb.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/blog3.png" width="750" height="250" /></a>TradeHero has been featured on some of our users’ blogs.\n\nHere’s a short recap of the reviews that we’ve received so far:\n<ol start="1">\n	<li><strong>BigFatPurse</strong>: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">http://www.bigfatpurse.com/2013/01/review-of-tradehero-virtual-vs-reality/</span></li>\n</ol>\n“TradeHero is easy for anyone to participate and accessible on-the-go with your phone.”\n\n<!--more-->\n<ol start="2">\n	<li><strong>Marubozu</strong>: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">http://mystocksinvesting.com/trade-hero/follow-my-trades-at-tradehero-marubozu1688/</span></li>\n</ol>\nFollow his portfolio on TradeHero for the “exact trade detail on the entry price, exit price and stop loss”.\n<ol>\n	<li><strong>Kiss Investing</strong>: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">http://kissinvesting.blogspot.sg/2013/02/tradehero-review-stock-market-app.html</span></li>\n</ol>\n“The <b><i>unique thing</i></b> about this App is that it combines both social networking and trading &amp; Good Traders can earn money from this!”\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe’ve received some great suggestions from them. Thanks to BigFatPurse, we’ve noticed that certain traders have been investing heavily in sub-penny stocks. Also, as James Yeo of KISS Investing pointed out, top traders are currently ranked only by ROI.  In next version, traders will be ranked by their skill – we have developed a special algorithm to determine this.\n\nLike how TradeHero sounds? Try it out for yourself! You can download it from the App Store here (<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tradehero-mobile/id572226383?ls=1&amp;mt=8">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tradehero-mobile/id572226383?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a>).\n\n&nbsp;', 'Blog Reviews'