(317, 4, '2013-06-21 16:53:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '&nbsp;\n\nWe''re back! And today, we will be discussing and explaining the second analysis of choosing a Stock: Technical Analysis.\n<h2>Technical Analysis</h2>\nTechnical Analysis involves graphical chart readings according to past prices and movements in the market. It is not absolute, but investors use this method to predict and anticipate on future trends. In this analysis, the forces of demand and supply play major parts in determining the price.', 'How to Choose A Stock: Technical Analysis', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2013-06-21 16:53:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=317', 0, 'post', '', 0),
