(1767, 3, '2015-03-13 14:39:59', '2015-03-13 06:39:59', '<h2>What is it?</h2>\r\n<p>Ever wanted a fun, risk-free way to learn about investing in the stock market? Play SGX StockWhiz 2015 and try your hand at stock investing using virtual currency. It’s the perfect way to get started if you’ve never invested in stocks before but always wanted to. Compete against investor across South East Asia and stand a chance to win cash prizes and keep your virtual profits as Commission Credits sponsored by OCBC Securities. What’s more, you can discuss your favourite stocks, learn the basics of investing with fun videos, access the latest stock news and alerts follow top performing traders for advice. So take the first step to learn about investment – Join SGX StockWhiz 2015 today and play on-the-go by downloading the TradeHero mobile app.</p>\r\n<h2>How to play?</h2>\r\n<p>You can play SGX StockWhiz 2015 using the “TradeHero” app on your iOS or Android mobile.</p>', 'SGX StockWhiz 2015', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sgxstockwhiz2015', '', '', '2015-08-20 03:44:18', '2015-08-20 03:44:18', '', 0, 'http://en.tradehero.mobi/?page_id=1767', 0, 'page', '', 0),
