(1848, 3, '2015-04-30 11:35:13', '2015-04-30 03:35:13', '<h2>What is it?</h2>\r\n<p>Ever wanted a fun, risk-free way to learn about investing in the Foreign Exchange (FX) market? TradeHero has collaborated with OANDA on it''s first ever virtual FX Trading competition. Play the OANDA FX Challenge and try your hand at FX trading using virtual currency. It’s the perfect way to get started if you’ve never traded in FX before but always wanted to. Pit yourself against top FX traders on TradeHero, emerge as the top trader, and win cash prizes. What’s more, you can discuss your favourite picks, learn the basics of trading FX with fun videos, access the latest FX news and alerts, follow top performing traders for advice. So take the first step to learn about FX – Join the OANDA FX Challenge today and play on-the-go by downloading the TradeHero mobile app.</p>\r\n<h2>How to play?</h2>\r\n<p>You can play OANDA FX Challenge using the “TradeHero” app on your iOS or Android mobile.</p>', 'OANDA FX Challenge', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oanda-fx-challenge', '', '', '2015-08-20 03:32:02', '2015-08-20 03:32:02', '', 0, 'http://en.tradehero.mobi/?page_id=1848', 0, 'page', '', 0),
