(2039, 1, '2015-07-31 10:47:45', '2015-07-31 10:47:45', '<p><strong>* Must have:</strong> Deep knowledge of Microsoft C#, LINQ, Entity Framework, Web MVC... full-stack cross-platform engineering: front to back. If this holds no fear for you, then get in touch.</p>\n							<p><strong>* Desirable:</strong> Knowledge of financial markets data models - pricing feeds, trade and position table structures and experience in first-line external support with good oral and written communication skills.</p>\n							<p><strong>Bottom line:</strong> if you''re passionate about working in a high performance engineering team, then <a href="mailto:hiring@tradehero.mobi"><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></a>! We''re taking submissions at all experience levels and we can tailor the role for the right candidate. But spots are limited. Bring your a-game, or stay at home.</p>\n							<p><strong>Step one:</strong> block aside two hours of your time... prove your skills by answering the four algorithm questions here. You can answer in any mainstream language, but be warned the questions are TOUGH. We suggest you take the practice question (on the Codility homepage) before you take on the main questions.</p>\n							<p>&lt;<a href="https://codility.com/honeypot/TradeHero-Pte-Ltd-Apr2014">https://codility.com/honeypot/TradeHero-Pte-Ltd-Apr2014</a>&gt;</p>\n							<p><strong>Step two:</strong> email us with you CV and tell us what excites you in tech, what you''ve done that you''re proud of, what you would bring to the team.</p>\n							<p>We love working with true talent, with those who have a PASSION and a deep interest in technology. Got what it takes? Then get in touch now.</p>\n							<h4>Key Responsibilities</h4>\n							<ul>\n								<li>Support of existing Social Trading</li>\n								<li>Development and support of new features and functionality as required by Product and Business development teams</li>\n								<li>Deliver new server and client components as per evolving business requirements</li>\n								<li>Discuss requirements with Product and Business Development Teams</li>\n								<li>Live Production support and troubleshooting of critical problems. </li>\n							</ul>\n							<h4>What to expect at TradeHero:</h4>\n							<ul>\n								<li>Opportunity to work with an excellent multi-national team with decades of investment banking, entrepreneurial, marketing and engineering experience INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
