s-04''\r\ntitle=''FOLLOW TOP TRADERS''\r\n]Top Traders will become “DW Heroes” who you can follow on the leaderboard. Get inside the Heroes’ minds by following their winning trades on the TradeHero app. Apply the strategies that you learn in real time.\r\n[/learning_feature]\r\n\r\n[learning_feature\r\nicon=''icon-education-science-03''\r\ntitle=''FREE WARRANT TRAINING ONLINE''\r\n]The DW Hero Investor Academy provides everything you need to know about DW. Watch short video tutorials or visit Macquarie’s interactive website to learn as you go! You can also join us at our complimentary seminars.\r\n<div class="btn btn-link"><a href="https://www.mqwarrants.co.th/flash/edu/th/mq_education_th.html">Video tutorials</a></div>\r\n<div class="btn btn-link"><a href="https://www.mqwarrants.co.th/tools?sp=dwscreener">Find your DWs</a></div>\r\n<div class="btn btn-link"><a href="https://www.mqwarrants.co.th/seminars">Seminar</a></div>\r\n[/learning_feature]\r\n\r\n[learning_features_close]', 'Macquarie DW Hero', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1411-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-19 09:45:02', '2015-08-19 09:45:02', '', 1411, 'http://thweb.local/1411-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
