(2331, 1, '2015-08-20 03:52:43', '2015-08-20 03:52:43', '<h2>What is it?</h2>\n<p>Trade Hero is a mobile application that provides a real time simulation of trading on the stock market. Once downloaded, you can join the first ever Virtual Warrants competition organised in Malaysia, Warrant Hero and compete for RM 100,000 in cash prizes. It’s the perfect way to learn about one of the fastest growing investment tools in Malaysia.</p>\n<h2>How to play?</h2>\n<p>You can play the Warrant Hero using the “TradeHero” app on your iOS or Android mobile.</p>\n[learning_feature\nicon=''icon-faces-users-04''\ntitle=''FOLLOW TOP TRADERS''\n]Top Traders will become “Warrant Heroes” who you can follow on the leaderboard. Get inside the Heroes’ minds by following their winning trades on the TradeHero app. Apply the strategies that you learnt in real time.\n[/learning_feature]\n\n[learning_feature\nicon=''icon-education-science-03''\ntitle=''FREE WARRANT TRAINING ONLINE''\n]The Warrant Hero Investor Academy provides everything you need to know about Warrant. Watch short video tutorials or visit Macquarie’s interactive website to learn as you go! You can also join us at our complimentary seminars.\n<div class="btn btn-link"><a href="https://www.malaysiawarrants.com.my/speaker">Video tutorials</a></div>\n<div class="btn btn-link"><a href="https://www.malaysiawarrants.com.my/tools?sp=dwsearch">Find your Warrants</a></div>\n<div class="btn btn-link"><a href="https://www.malaysiawarrants.com.my/seminars">Seminar</a></div>\n[/learning_feature]\n\n[learning_features_close]', 'Warrant Hero Malaysia', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1940-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-08-20 03:52:43', '2015-08-20 03:52:43', '', 1940, 'http://thweb.local/1940-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
